categories       devel
maintainers      toby
description      Berkeley Yacc
long_description \
	Berkeley Yacc (byacc) is generally conceded to \
	be the best yacc variant available. In contrast \
	to bison, it is written to avoid dependencies \
	upon a particular compiler.
